{"tid":1046300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美敍聯軍發動滅IS關鍵一役","createTime":"2019-03-04T06:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T10:51:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f111bb83607341acbed61f53d786d231a1c6849c","tid":1046300,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T06:50:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190304/20625389\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190304%2F20625389&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4EbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=d0d2ce56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190304%2F20625389&h=4f35a280\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190304/20625389</a><br />\n<br />\n美敍聯軍發動滅IS關鍵一役<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190304/large/a1302a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190304%2Flarge%2Fa1302a.gif&h=f433aa77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圍攻巴古茲的SDF戰士為車上機關槍上彈。路透社<br />\n<br />\n獲美國支持的「敍利亞民主力量」（SDF）上周五開始攻進「伊斯蘭國」（IS）最後據點巴古茲後，因面對IS武裝分子頑強抵抗，只能緩緩推進；但他們估計昨天會可發動「決定性一役」，殲滅IS僅餘勢力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：IS殘兵怒斥領袖跳船逃遁沙漠<br />\n<br />\nIS佈下重重地雷<br />\n<br />\n隨IS控制地逐步萎縮，數千名武裝分子和IS追隨者帶平民退到巴古茲一帶村落和農地，近周出動作最後反抗。SDF發言人蓋米什盧指，「我方部隊正以緩慢速度推進，來避免任何問題，因IS在該處佈下了重重地雷。只是一小塊地，沿路就已埋下數千個地雷」。<br />\n<br />\n蓋米什盧又指，堅持死守巴古茲的武裝分子通常是外國人，他們會用隧道藏身，然後進行突襲。SDF指揮官阿邁迪同指，地面部隊攻入IS據點時，IS武裝分子會以佈下的詭雷和狙擊步槍還擊。IS昨又頻以人肉炸彈和自殺式汽車炸彈，拖慢SDF推進。<br />\n<br />\n美國為首聯軍則繼續向巴古茲發動空襲，以配合SDF地面部隊進攻。敍利亞通訊社指聯軍前日在巴古茲發動空襲時，採用了國際禁用的白磷彈，「陷數百名平民及IS人質入險境」。敍國曾多次指摘聯軍使用白磷彈，但美國否認。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美聯社/新華社  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190304/large/a1302b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190304%2Flarge%2Fa1302b.gif&h=7abcad94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被困孤兒和平民近日陸續撤出巴古茲。路透社<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190304/large/a1302c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190304%2Flarge%2Fa1302c.gif&h=b616ad0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重獲自由的雅茲迪男孩跟家人相擁。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n前後被擄7次 飽受虐待 大命IS人質 避過兩次斬首<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\nIS殘兵怒斥領袖跳船逃遁沙漠<br />\n<br />\nIS殘兵怒斥領袖跳船逃遁沙漠<br />\n聖戰新娘丈夫盼與妻兒回荷蘭<br />\n前後被擄7次 飽受虐待大命IS人質 避過兩次斬首"},{"pid":"8c59cdcce0b1d63248cca975f9945e00c02a2b65","tid":1046300,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T10:51:23.000Z","msg":"SDF-1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}